This tool extracts the company name from a user's message and validates whether the company meets the criteria for
financial analysis. The company must be publicly traded and listed on either the NASDAQ or NYSE. If the company meets
these two conditions, the tool returns a true value. If the company fails to meet any of the conditions, the tool
returns a false value along with an error message specifying which condition was not met.


